{"tid":532826,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"酒店泳池遭200磅泳客「炸水」撞傷 英男結婚周年度假變噩夢","createTime":"2018-01-18T08:07:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T05:05:27.000Z","uid":75969,"like":94,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"e5b867d9399c35f71a857ea3f8cb1e3c85c32321","tid":532826,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T08:07:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c60IK8jpXIw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dc60IK8jpXIw&d=s09NBRW2RjhpgeTTQya5GpUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=b1c9767d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c60IK8jpXIw</a><br />\n<br />\n英國一名男子在巴塞隆拿旅遊時遭遇罕見意外，在酒店泳池被重95公斤（209磅）的「炸水」大漢撞傷。<br />\n<br />\n44歲的海德（Graham Hyde）去年6月與妻女度假兼慶祝結婚周年，在Alegria Pineda Splash酒店泳池的滑梯滑下時，突然一名男子像飛將軍一樣，屁股落到他身上，令他在水底360度打轉，當時更以為頸已斷。他被救起後由救傷車送院，證實頸與上背肌肉受傷。<br />\n<br />\n海德表示，那次無妄之災不但令假期遽然而終，出院後要「自生自滅」，返酒店遇着的士罷駛，令他要戴着頸箍在悶熱街頭受一小時煎熬。回家後，雖繼續接受物理治療，但多月後依然感到痛楚。<br />\n<br />\n海德不滿旅行社對他的情況不聞不問，決定對旅行社採取法律行動。<br />\n<br />\n英國《太陽報》  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180118/57721601\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180118%2F57721601&d=s09NBRW2RjhpgeTTQya5GpUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=8eb21222\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180118%2F57721601&h=65903c11\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180118/57721601</a>"},{"pid":"724b69edc728b185e94aa3cf00701ff68bcafe8c","tid":532826,"uid":149978,"like":66,"dislike":0,"score":66,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T08:12:42.000Z","msg":"明顯係設計管理失誤，冇整圍欄唔俾人入。"},{"pid":"fc8fffb161043d2f0976aa0953a26d94f39c7cf5","tid":532826,"uid":4180,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T09:17:39.000Z","msg":"睇左幾次, 真係好準<img src=\"/assets/faces/n